                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>Two fragments, which adjoin, but do not join perfectly, of the local 'travertino', forming a rectangular block, the original size and form/function of which is unclear. The fragments were found separately and the break is not recent. Fragment (a) is broken to left and right, but appears to be intact above and below; fragment (b) is intact along the lower edge, but broken on the other three sides. (a) is W 50 cm x H 34.5 cm x D 16; (b) is W 50 cm x H 30 cm x D 17 cm.</p>
